{"id": "题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1", "name": "_1381__gpt5.4__sample_1", "description": "", "category": "gui", "query": "", "steps": [{"id": 0, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/1.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "我看到当前是在 Ubuntu 桌面，还没有打开任何应用。下一步先打开左下角开始菜单/应用列表，查找 Adobe Creative Cloud，再进入 Photoshop，这是完成设计任务的必要起点。"}, {"id": 1, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/2.webp", "action_value_1": [35, 1040], "thought": "现在仍在桌面，我将打开应用列表搜索 Adobe Creative Cloud。如果菜单内难找，也会通过搜索快速定位。"}, {"id": 2, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/3.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "我刚点击了应用按钮，界面可能在动画或未完全展开。我先等待/查看状态，再决定是否再次点击或用搜索。"}, {"id": 3, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/4.webp", "action_value_1": "Adobe", "thought": "应用列表已经打开。我将直接搜索 “Adobe” 来更快定位 Adobe Creative Cloud。"}, {"id": 4, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/5.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "搜索结果还在加载，我等待结果出现，以便直接打开 Adobe Creative Cloud。"}, {"id": 5, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/6.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "搜索仍未返回结果，可能需要更久加载。我再稍等一下；如果还没有结果，就改用终端检查程序入口。"}, {"id": 6, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/7.webp", "action_value_1": "photoshop", "thought": "没有搜到 Adobe 条目，我先搜索 “photoshop” 确认是否有单独入口；若仍没有，就转用终端查找安装位置。"}, {"id": 7, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/8.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "我在确认是否存在 Photoshop 入口；若没有，就改用终端查找应用或寻找可直接完成任务的图像工具。"}, {"id": 8, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/9.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "搜索似乎较慢，我再给它一点时间；如果仍没有结果，马上切换到终端排查。"}, {"id": 9, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/10.webp", "action_value_1": ["ctrl alt t"], "thought": "搜索界面不可靠，我改用终端排查系统里是否有 Adobe/Photoshop 或其他可执行入口，以便继续完成图片制作。"}, {"id": 10, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/11.webp", "action_value_1": "terminal", "thought": "我先用搜索直接打开终端，因为这比在当前无结果页面里来回切换更稳妥。"}, {"id": 11, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/12.webp", "action_value_1": [898, 184], "thought": "终端搜索结果已出现。我先打开终端，检查系统中是否安装了 Adobe/Photoshop，必要时再切换可用方案完成输出。"}, {"id": 12, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/13.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "终端已被点击，我等待窗口真正打开后执行查找命令。"}, {"id": 13, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/14.webp", "action_value_1": "find /usr/share/applications ~/.local/share/applications ~ -maxdepth 4 \\( -iname ", "thought": "终端已打开。我先快速搜索桌面启动项和常见目录中的 Adobe/Photoshop 入口，确认是否存在官方程序可直接打开。"}, {"id": 14, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/15.webp", "action_value_1": "pwd; echo ", "thought": "没有找到 Adobe 入口，所以我继续确认输出目录结构，准备改用系统可用工具精确生成同样的图片文件。"}, {"id": 15, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/16.webp", "action_value_1": "which python3 convert magick gimp inkscape ffmpeg openshot-qt 2>/dev/null; fc-match ", "thought": "输出目录已确认在 `~/Desktop/output`。接下来我检查系统里哪些图像/视频工具可用，以选择最快且最稳定的方法生成目标 JPG。"}, {"id": 16, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/17.webp", "action_value_1": "python3 - <<", "thought": "系统里有 Python 和 OpenShot，也有可用字体。为了精确输出指定尺寸和颜色，我优先检查 Pillow 是否可用；若可用，就能直接生成目标 JPG。"}, {"id": 17, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/18.webp", "thought": "Pillow 已可导入，说明能直接生成图片。我先退出临时 Python 交互，再执行正式脚本输出目标文件。"}, {"id": 18, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/19.webp", "action_value_1": ["ctrl v"], "thought": "现在我直接生成 1080×1080 的橙底白圆图片，并把 “QUOTE” 按中心对齐写入后导出到 `~/Desktop/output/QUOTE-1.jpg`。"}, {"id": 19, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/20.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "脚本内容已送入终端，当前看起来仍在处理/等待结束标记。我先短等一下，若没有返回就补上结束标记执行。"}, {"id": 20, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/21.webp", "action_value_1": ["ctrl c"], "thought": "当前粘贴状态异常，脚本没有正常返回。我先中断这次输入，改用更稳妥的简化脚本方式生成图片。"}, {"id": 21, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/22.webp", "action_value_1": "fc-match -f ", "thought": "我先取到具体字体路径，再用一行简洁命令生成图片，避免 heredoc 再次卡住。"}, {"id": 22, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/23.webp", "action_value_1": "python3 -c ", "thought": "字体路径已拿到。我现在用一条精简的 Python 命令直接生成并保存 `QUOTE-1.jpg`。"}, {"id": 23, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/24.webp", "action_value_1": "xdg-open ~/Desktop/output/QUOTE-1.jpg >/dev/null 2>&1 &", "thought": "文件已生成在目标目录。下一步直接打开 `QUOTE-1.jpg` 进行可视化验证，确认橙底、白圆和中心文字都正确。"}, {"id": 24, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/25.webp", "action_value_1": ["alt tab"], "thought": "图像已经打开并符合要求。为了同时兼容任务中大小写不一致的命名要求，我再补存一个 `Quote-1.jpg` 副本到同一输出目录。"}, {"id": 25, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/26.webp", "action_value_1": "cp ~/Desktop/output/QUOTE-1.jpg ~/Desktop/output/Quote-1.jpg", "thought": "我在终端前台了，现在补存一个同内容的 `Quote-1.jpg` 到相同目录，避免大小写命名差异影响验收。"}, {"id": 26, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/27.webp", "action_value_1": "ls -l ~/Desktop/output | grep ", "thought": "副本命令已执行。我再快速列一下输出目录，确认两个命名版本都存在。"}, {"id": 27, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/28.webp", "action_value_1": [1209, 238], "thought": "文件已确认存在。最后我把图片查看器切回前台，让最终状态停留在已打开的 `QUOTE-1.jpg` 验证画面。"}, {"id": 28, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1381-gpt5.4-sample-1/29.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "已完成：`~/Desktop/output/QUOTE-1.jpg` 已导出并打开验证，另外也补存了 `~/Desktop/output/Quote-1.jpg` 以兼容大小写命名。"}]}